column3: “Awesome, focused high. You'll want to get stuff done around the house. Also makes you very talkative and gives you the want to share ideas. Overall very nice strain if you want to be philosophical.”
“Decent taste, nice high.. didn't really feel couch ridden" but decent body high.”"

“Love it, it's absolutely the one of the best inventions they have ever made. I got the Concentrate, the CO2 Vaporizer Cartridge so it is a lot different than smoking the flower. if you have not tried one of the Vape Cartridge's I suggest you go try one NOW! They have them and other strains in the Vape Cartridges as well all at Miller's Marijuana in Porter Wa right by Elma.”
